% Future syntax: the `Prov` annotation asks for full provenance — the pedigree
% of every derived fact as a compiled circuit (режим B by knowledge compilation,
% SDD/WMC). The grammar accepts it; the engine does not build it yet, so the
% checker refuses it by name with a stable code — a future-syntax frame.
domain firm.
pred owns(firm, firm): Bool.
pred controls(firm, firm): Prov.
controls(X, Y) :- owns(X, Y).
